== Ubuzima bwo hambere ==
Ngardy Conteh George yavukiye iFreetown, Sierra Leone kandi ni umuhererezi mu bana bane. Mu bwana bwe, umuryango we wimukiye i Toronto, muri Kanada mu 1981. Conteh George yagiye mu ishuri rya Leta rya Jesse Ketchum (1981-1992), n'Amashuri yisumbuye y'Amajyaruguru (1992-1995) mbere yo kurangiza mu kigo cya Vaughan Road Collegiate Institute (1995-1997).

== Kurikirana n'umurima ==
Conteh George yize muri kaminuza ya New Orleans (1997-2001) kuri bourse yo gusiganwa ku maguru aho yitabiriye amarushanwa yo gusimbuka gatatu no gusimbuka hejuru .  Conteh George yegukanye umwanya wa 3 mu gusimbuka hejuru muri Shampiyona yo mu nzu ya Sunbelt 1998. Mu 2001, Ihuriro rya Sun Belt ryatangaje ko Ngardy Conteh yari mu rutonde rw’abakomiseri 2000-2001 na Academic Honor Roll. <ref name=":1" /> Urutonde rwabakomiseri ni icyegeranyo cyabakinnyi babanyeshuri bakomeje byibuze amanota 3,5 mugihembwe cyambere cyangwa bitatu bya gatatu.

== Umwuga wa film ==
Nyuma yo guhabwa impamyabumenyi, Conteh George yibanze ku gutunganya amafilime no kuvuga amateka ya Diaspora nyafurika . <ref>https://africanfilmny.org/directors/ngardy-conteh-george/</ref> Filime ye ya mbere yari ''Abasirikare kumihanda'' (yakozwe muri gahunda ya Momentum hamwe na NFB mu 2004) yasobanuye imbaraga za Ras King zo kwigisha no guha imbaraga urubyiruko.) <ref>http://onf-nfb.gc.ca/en/our-collection/?idfilm=51675</ref> mu 2005, Conteh George yari umuyobozi ushinzwe gutunganya inyandiko. urukurikirane rw'ibitabo ''bizima'', byakozwe na Frances Ann Solomon . Yayoboye ibice 3 kandi afatanya kuyobora kimwe muri byo. <ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm2075341/</ref>

Hamwe na sosiyete ye Mattru Media, Conteh George yakoze, ayobora kandi ahindura imishinga myinshi yo gutangaza no kugana abakiriya. Mu bicuruzwa harimo ''The Rhyming Chef Barbuda,'' igitaramo cyo guteka gihuza ibiryo hamwe na hip hop yakinnye numugabo we Philman George. Yasohoye ibihe bibiri byikinyamakuru cyimyidagaduro yerekana ikinamico hip-hop yerekana <nowiki><i id="mwMw">Cypher</i></nowiki> kuri TV ya AUX, igice cyisaha yisaha ya ''The Circle of Slavery'' yerekanwe bwa mbere mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Siyera Lewone, hamwe na documentaire ndende ya The Flying Stars (Yiswe ' Leone Stars ') <ref>https://www.thestar.com/life/travel/2008/10/18/chef_cooks_with_rhythm_rhyme_and_a_dash_of_thyme.html</ref> <ref>https://www.harbourfrontcentre.com/worldroutes/festivals.cfm?id=2209&festival_id=64</ref> <ref name=":2">https://realscreen.com/2011/09/13/tiff-2011-leone-stars-wins-tiffs-pitch-this/</ref>

=== Inyenyeri ziguruka ===
''Flying Stars'' (muburyo bwa ''Leone Stars'' ) iyobowe kandi ikorwa na Conteh George na Allan Tong hamwe nabandi ba producer ni Katarina Soukup wo muri Catbird Productions. Umushinga wakusanyije amadolari ibihumbi 20 kuri kickstarter kandi niyo documentaire yambere yatsindiye Telefilm Canada TIFF Pitch Iyi! amarushanwa. <ref name=":2">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://realscreen.com/2011/09/13/tiff-2011-leone-stars-wins-tiffs-pitch-this/ "TIFF 2011: "Leone Stars" wins TIFF's Pitch This!"]. ''REALSCREEN''.</cite></ref> <ref>https://www.cbc.ca/news/entertainment/doc-tale-of-amputee-soccer-players-wins-pitch-this-1.1108412</ref> Nyuma yo gutsinda, film yakiriye inkunga yikigega cya Sundance Institute Documentary Film Fund. <ref>https://www.sundance.org/blogs/news/29-documentaries-receive-582000-in-grants-from-sundance-institute-documenta</ref> Mu mpeshyi ya 2012 film yatoranijwe muri Hoteri ya Hot Docs . <ref>https://playbackonline.ca/2011/09/13/tiff-2011-leone-stars-wins-pitch-this/</ref> <ref>https://realscreen.com/2012/03/27/hot-docs-reveals-forum-picks/</ref> Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere ku isi muri RIDM ikomeza gukina mu  Iserukiramuco rya Filime zabirabura harimo irya Toronto na Wilson Oakville, ndetse n'Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Black Star . <ref>https://catbirdproductions.ca/en/news/world-premiere-of-the-flying-stars-at-the-ridm</ref> <ref>https://www.timeout.com/toronto/things-to-do/the-flying-stars-toronto-premiere</ref> <ref>https://www.oyamediagroup.com/original-content/the-flying-stars</ref> Iri serukiramuco ryasojwe nigihembo cyiza cya documentaire mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya BronzeLens 2015 kandi ryatangajwe ku isi yose harimo Umuyoboro wa Documentaire muri Kanada, NHK mu Buyapani, DR muri Danimarike na Al Jazeera . Ubu iratemba kuri Kweli. TV ku isi hose.  <ref>http://www6.nhk.or.jp/wdoc/backnumber/detail/?pid=170329</ref> <ref>https://www.aljazeera.com/program/witness/2015/9/13/the-flying-stars</ref> <ref>https://www.cbc.ca/programguide/program/the_flying_stars</ref>

=== Itsinda ry'itangazamakuru rya OYA ===
Mu mwaka wa 2016, Conteh George yayoboye kandi ahindura inyandiko ngufi ya ''Dudley Avuga kuri njye'' mu rwego rwo kuyobora umushinga wa Akua Benjamin Legacy Project yakozwe na Alison Duke . Yakiriye Ikiganiro Cyiza cya Kanada mu Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime ya Karayibe. <ref>https://www.ryerson.ca/akua-benjamin-project/what-is-the-legacy-project/</ref> <ref>https://www.ryerson.ca/akua-benjamin-project/watch-50-years-of-black-activism/</ref> <ref>https://nowtoronto.com/news/black-heroes-of-toronto-anti-racism</ref> Abagore bombi barema bashizeho ubufatanye bushingiye ku guhuza indangagaciro maze bashinga uruganda rukora OYA Media Group. <ref>https://www.oyamediagroup.com/oya</ref> Itsinda rya mbere rya OYA Media Group ni ''Mr. Jane and Finch''bayobowe na Conteh George kandi bafatanije kwandika / bafatanije na Conteh George na Duke. Iyi documentaire yashinzwe na CBC Doc POV ikazenguruka kuri Winston Larose, umukunzi w’umukecuru w’imyaka 80 ukomoka mu gihugu cya Giyane-Kanada ujugunya ingofero muri politiki y’ibanze kandi ahura n’ivanguramoko rishingiye kuri gahunda muri politiki ya Kanada. <ref>https://www.cbc.ca/cbcdocspov/episodes/mr-jane-and-finch</ref> Iyi filime yatorewe igihembo cya Golden Sheaf kandi yahawe ibihembo bibiri bya Canadian Screen Awards : Igihembo cya Donald Brittain Award Cyiza Cy’Imibereho Myiza ya Politiki no Kwandika neza kuri Documentaire. <ref>{{Template:Cite web}}http://yorktonfilm.com/2019-winners-nominees/mr_jane_and_finch/</ref> <ref>https://www.vimooz.com/2020/06/18/oya-media-groups-mr-jane-and-finch-wins-2-canadian-screen-awards/</ref>

Yashinzwe na Duke, abo bagore bombi bayobora kandi gahunda ya OYA Emerging Filmmaker (bisanzwe byitwa Black Youth Pathway to Industry) kubakiri bato barangije porogaramu za firime na tereviziyo. <ref>https://mag.women2elevate.club/issue-18/whats-happening-now-oya-media-group</ref>

